{"tid":1532691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈係時候為呢場抗爭起名，叫做《時水革命》！！","createTime":"2019-09-02T14:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T15:26:34.000Z","uid":294095,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3ebd370f073b83dca87342f909513517346784ad","tid":1532691,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:57:24.000Z","msg":"由六月到九月呢一刻，唔知有幾多手足流血、被捕、犠牲...<br />\n呢場抗爭係注定要刻入<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港史書</span></span></strong>入面<br />\n估唔到係呢場分散式冇大台抗爭入面，三個月都未有一個通用名字<br />\n<br />\n金融時報已經將呢場抗爭正名英文名字<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《Water Revolution》</span></span></strong><br />\n中文名各位仍然眾說紛紜，叫《水革命》係有啲失霸氣，叫《流水革命》意義上好似流動勝於堅守，永遠嘅流動係唔會得到最終嘅勝利！我哋要堅持香港呢一片土地！叫《流水革命》限制咗我哋嘅想像力！<br />\n<br />\n所以我係度正式提議，呢場抗爭應該叫做<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《時水革命》</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n原因有二<br />\n一、時水，字面解釋上係應時的雨水。呢場抗爭的確係來的非常及時。適逢中美貿易戰及台灣大選，呢場抗爭正係百年一遇嘅時機中萌芽，呢場雨水來的非常及時，為呢片腐爛無比嘅土地提供重生的機會<br />\n字典︰ <a href=\"http://www.chinesewords.org/dict/148959-226.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinesewords.org%2Fdict%2F148959-226.html&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1ahPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=85bcf0c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinesewords.org/dict/148959-226.html</a><br />\n二、係不知不覺間，呢場抗爭泛起了《光復香港，時代革命》嘅口號，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">《時代革命》</span></span></strong> 加上直譯嘅 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">《水革命》</span></span></strong>，自然就係&hellip;<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《時水革命》</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6b12f49692bffea1bc9746a9fafbc14a7d8ee03f","tid":1532691,"uid":7903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:58:30.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲實會叫做屎水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0854cb0b5ed90017bff0f173fbaac35e053b640","tid":1532691,"uid":30528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:58:49.000Z","msg":"唔制，好難聽。"},{"pid":"e706e9c491e8c1f6b49fbe271a7c3413be37a78e","tid":1532691,"uid":161541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf8d21014cd751f98f1bfc967f953ea0feace50","tid":1532691,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"屎水咩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫林鄭之亂好過啦<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵職員<br />\n今日你包庇<br />\n他日你自己必定遭殃</span></strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">譴責黨鐵 黑箱作業<br />\n放警入閘 狂毆乘客</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b8d86e75b94d29d5447c3778210b67998742848f","tid":1532691,"uid":2766,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:59:40.000Z","msg":"得罪講句<br />\n幾時由你改名咁巴弊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6bc312f97179e06bd5725052f4c07855bd6d43","tid":1532691,"uid":315587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:00:32.000Z","msg":"《流水革命》好聽D"},{"pid":"64127b5042b7a05951da5956680b18835dd199cb","tid":1532691,"uid":262190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b12f49692bffea1bc9746a9fafbc14a7d8ee03f","tid":1532691,"uid":7903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:58:30.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲實會叫做屎水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr